%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia%20Should%20Also%20Stand%20Behind%20Palestinians%26quot%3B%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20under%20fire%20for%20its%20statement%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20the%20party's%20senior%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20said%20today%20that%20the%20terror%20group%20does%20not%20represent%20Palestine.%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20should%20not%20forget%20the%20cause%20of%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20so%20far%20--%20judging%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Tweets%20--%20has%20taken%20a%20stand%20unambiguously%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Israelis%20who%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20this%20unjust%20and%20inhumane%20attack%20by%20the%20Hamas.%20That's%20fine%20as%20far%20as%20it%20goes.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20go%20far%20enough%20because%20there%20is%20a%20broader%20picture%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20missing%20from%20the%20traditional%20Indian%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20India's%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20that%20started%20with%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20continued%20till%20the%20UPA%20government%20led%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20today%2C%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%2C%20the%20party's%20highest-decision-making%20body%2C%20had%20expressed%20its%20%26quot%3Bdismay%20and%20anguish%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20war.%20But%20it%20also%20underscored%20the%20Palestinian%20people's%20right%20to%20%26quot%3Bland%20(and)%20self-government%2C%20and%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%20and%20respect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20came%20under%20BJP%20attack%2C%20with%20the%20party%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20supporting%20terrorism%20and%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostage%20to%20minority%20vote%20bank%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress's%20CWC%20resolution%20on%20the%20Israel%20war%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20how%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20was%20hostage%20to%20Congress's%20minority%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20until%20Modi%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20not%20support%20the%20formation%20of%20Israel%20till%201950%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%20after%20the%20Jewish%20state%20came%20into%20being%2C%20since%20Nehru%2C%20having%20experienced%20the%20horrors%20of%20partition%2C%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20another%20nation%20on%20religious%20lines.%20There%20was%20also%20concern%20about%20Muslim%20sensitivities%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20India's%20stance%20began%20to%20change%20slowly%20with%20its%20growing%20affinity%20to%20the%20US.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20today%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20have%20as%20much%20right%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20as%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20broader%20policy%20which%20should%20have%20been%20affirmed%20which%20is%20that%20of%20equal%20rights%20of%20both%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20to%20live%20in%20peace%2C%20security%20and%20dignity%20behind%20safe%20borders%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20time%20since%20the%20peace%20initiatives%20a%20Century%20ago%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20side%2C%20particularly%20the%20PLO%20(Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation)%20headquartered%20in%20Ramallah%20has%20been%20keeping%20its%20end%20of%20the%20bargain%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20Israeli%20side%20that%20hasn't%20been%20doing%20do%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20and%20%26quot%3Bdehumanizing%20activities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697024580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Furh2n8_shashi-tharoor-ndtv-650_650x400_11_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-also-stand-behind-palestinians-shashi-tharoor-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-war-4471054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20under%20fire%20for%20its%20statement%20on%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20the%20party's%20senior%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20said%20today%20that%20the%20terror%20group%20does%20not%20represent%20Palestine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-also-stand-behind-palestinians-shashi-tharoor-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-war-4471054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-also-stand-behind-palestinians-shashi-tharoor-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-war-4471054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-should-also-stand-behind-palestinians-shashi-tharoor-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-war-4471054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Recalls%20How%20She%20Escaped%20Hamas%20Attack%20Dodging%20Bullets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20a%20British-Israeli%20woman%20said%20that%20she%20had%20to%20escape%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20open%20fields%20and%20past%20army%20forces%26quot%3B%20as%20there%20was%20an%20ongoing%20gun%20battle%20in%20Yated%2C%20Israel.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20son%20was%20heading%20for%20the%20front%20line%20to%20join%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fbritish-israeli-mother-tells-of-harrowing-escape-from-hamas-fighters-wfv02xk0x%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Following%20a%20complete%20evacuation%2C%20Yated%20is%20currently%20one%20of%20several%20communities%20designated%20as%20a%20closed%20military%20zone.%20Dozens%20of%20people%20are%20reported%20missing%20or%20presumed%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDebby%20Shharon%2C%20a%20British%20national%20with%20four%20children%2C%20sought%20refuge%20in%20their%20family's%20safe%20house%20when%20gunfire%20erupted%20in%20their%20town%2C%20a%20settlement%20of%20120%20households%20situated%20approximately%202.5%20miles%20from%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20was%20crammed%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20their%20daughter%20and%20son-in-law%2C%20their%20autistic%20son%2C%20and%20three%20grandkids%20under%20the%20age%20of%20eleven%2C%20in%20a%20three-by-two-metre%20room%20for%20roughly%2036%20hours.%20They%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20was%20going%20on%20outside%20of%20their%20house%20in%20southern%20Israel.%20They%20were%20also%20without%20electricity%20and%20their%20phone%20batteries%20were%20running%20low%20hours%20into%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20in%20those%20hours%20that%20I%20really%20understood%20the%20mentality%20my%20English%20mother%20had%20raised%20us%20with%20after%20having%20grown%20up%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20and%20how%20she%20taught%20us%20to%20behave%20in%20emergencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sharon%20said.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20situation%20appeared%20%26quot%3Bapocalyptic%26quot%3B%20and%20people%20were%20running%20all%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20could%20have%20prepared%20us%20for%20this.%20The%20idea%20of%20'keeping%20our%20chin%20up'%20and%20staying%20positive%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20chaos%20and%20uncertainty%3B%20I%20could%20see%20it%20all%20taking%20place%20in%20those%20moments.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20playing%20out%20all%20those%20stories%20my%20mother%20had%20told%20me%20growing%20up.%20Trying%20to%20keep%20the%20kids%20calm%2C%20to%20stop%20them%20screaming%2C%20to%20stop%20them%20leaving%2C%20all%20this%20while%20we%20are%20together%20in%20a%20safe%20room%2C%20which%20was%20designed%20to%20keep%20us%20safe%20from%20rockets%2C%20not%20from%20terrorists%2C%20so%20it%20didn't%20even%20lock%20from%20the%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20she%20has%20never%20seen%20this%20kind%20of%20conflict%20even%20though%20she%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Israel%20since%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20crazy%20to%20say%20it%20but%20the%20rocket%20attacks%20we%20lived%20with%20before%20are%20not%20hard%20for%20us%20any%20more%3B%20you%20don't%20feel%20it%20turns%20your%20life%20around%20-%20but%20when%20you%20know%20there%20are%20people%20around%20your%20house%20shooting%2C%20it%20is%20a%20different%20feeling%20altogether.%20I%20felt%20sick%20from%20the%20minute%20it%20started.%20You%20have%20all%20these%20thoughts%20of%20what%20could%20happen.%20If%20a%20rocket%20falls%20on%20you%2C%20there%20aren't%20that%20many%20alternatives%20of%20what%20could%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20radio%20reception%20and%20understanding%20the%20scale%20of%20war%2C%20Ms%20Sharon%20stated%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Btraumatised%26quot%3B.%20Speaking%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20she%20added%2C%26quot%3BI%20can't%20breathe%20yet%2C%20I%20can't%20sleep%20-%20and%20it's%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20admit%2C%20I'm%20traumatised.%20%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20still%20serving%20and%20clearing%20out%20the%20area%20of%20what's%20left%20of%20the%20worst%20kind%20of%20enemy%20that%20exists%20these%20days.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Sharon%20said%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20areas%20of%20Eshkol%20have%20been%20devastated%20by%20bombings%20and%20rockets%20by%20Hamas.%20She%20also%20informed%20that%20the%20family%20would%20return%20once%20the%20situation%20gets%20better.%20%26quot%3BLeaving%20isn't%20an%20option.%20It%20will%20take%20so%20much%20to%20build%20it%20up%20again%2C%20so%20many%20things%20have%20been%20diminished%20altogether%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20and%20getting%20through%20the%20trauma%3B%20learning%20how%20to%20sleep%20again%2C%20how%20to%20trust%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697024160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fg0vfacmg_israel-gaza-war-afp_625x300_10_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-recalls-how-she-escaped-hamas-attack-dodging-bullets-4471302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20she%20has%20never%20seen%20this%20kind%20of%20conflict%20even%20though%20she%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Israel%20since%20the%20age%20of%20five.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-recalls-how-she-escaped-hamas-attack-dodging-bullets-4471302%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-recalls-how-she-escaped-hamas-attack-dodging-bullets-4471302%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-recalls-how-she-escaped-hamas-attack-dodging-bullets-4471302%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WC%20Live%3A%20After%20Hardik's%20Strike%2C%20India%20Put%20Brakes%20On%20Afghanistan's%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20Afghanistan%2C%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20Live%20Updates%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hardik%20Pandya%20cleaned%20up%20Azmatullah%20Omarzai%20to%20provide%20India%20a%20crucial%20breakthrough.%20Hashmatullah%20Shahidi%20has%20been%20joined%20by%20Mohammad%20Nabi%20as%20three-down%20Afghanistan%20aim%20to%20post%20a%20competitive%20total%20against%20India%20in%20Delhi.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Shardul%20Thakur%20earlier%20picked%20a%20wicket%20each%20to%20put%20Afghanistan%20under%20pressure.%20Afghanistan%20skipper%20Hashmatullah%20Shahidi%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat.%20While%20Afghanistan%20m