%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Study%20Finds%20New%2C%20Leading%20Cause%20Of%20Skin%20Cancer%20Deaths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENon-melanoma%20skin%20cancers%20(NMSC)%2C%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20less%20serious%20form%20of%20skin%20condition%2C%20is%20causing%20more%20deaths%20across%20the%20world%20than%20melanoma%2C%20a%20new%20study%20has%20found.%20Melanoma%20was%20so%20far%20the%20most%20common%20cause%20of%20skin%20cancer%20deaths.%20The%20study%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20group%20of%20researchers%20in%20Europe%20who%20used%20data%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation's%20(WHO)%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer.%20The%20researchers%20found%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20incidence%26quot%3B%20of%20skin%20cancer%20in%20fair-skinned%20and%20elderly%20populations%20from%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20Australia%20and%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202020%2C%20NMSC%20accounted%20for%2078%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20skin%20cancer%20cases%2C%20resulting%20in%20over%2063%2C700%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Thierry%20Passeron%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20study%20and%20dermatologist%20at%20Nice%20University%20Hospital%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20contrast%2C%20melanoma%20caused%20an%20estimated%2057%2C000%20fatalities%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20The%20significantly%20higher%20incidence%20of%20NMSC%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20led%20to%20a%20more%20substantial%20overall%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESkin%20cancer%20is%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20cancer%20in%20both%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20one%20in%20five%20expected%20to%20develop%20it%20in%20their%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENMSC%20refers%20to%20the%20more%20common%20group%20that%20slowly%20develops%20in%20the%20upper%20layers%20of%20the%20skin.%20Melanoma%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20a%20type%20of%20skin%20cancer%20that%20can%20spread%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Passerson's%20team%20believes%20that%20NMSC%20is%20underreported%20due%20to%20which%20its%20true%20impact%20may%20be%20even%20higher%20than%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20cause%20of%20both%20is%20exposure%20to%20ultraviolet%20rays%2C%20which%20come%20from%20the%20sun%20and%20are%20used%20in%20tanning%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20get%20the%20message%20out%20that%20not%20only%20melanoma%20can%20be%20fatal%2C%20but%20NMSC%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20professor%20Passeron%20said%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%20of%20NMSC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UK's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1003673%5C%22%3ENational%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20sign%20is%20usually%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20lump%20or%20discoloured%20patch%20on%20the%20skin%20that%20persists%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20and%20slowly%20progresses%20over%20months%20or%20sometimes%20years.%20This%20is%20the%20cancer%2C%20or%20tumour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20cancerous%20lumps%20are%20red%20and%20firm%20and%20sometimes%20turn%20into%20ulcers%2C%20while%20cancerous%20patches%20are%20usually%20flat%20and%20scaly.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697023560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fskin-cancer_625x300_1528967241604.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fstudy-finds-new-leading-cause-of-skin-cancer-deaths-4471265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Non-melanoma%20skin%20cancers%20refers%20to%20the%20more%20common%20group%20that%20slowly%20develops%20in%20the%20upper%20layers%20of%20the%20skin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fstudy-finds-new-leading-cause-of-skin-cancer-deaths-4471265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscienc