sed%20to%20take%20days.%20But%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20motorable%20road%20to%20Lipulekh%2C%20the%20pilgrimage%20is%20set%20to%20become%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20Lipulekh%20Pass%2C%20Dharchula%20and%20Adi%20Kailash%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20scheduled%20visit%20to%20Uttarakhand%20tomorrow.%20Next%20to%20Lipulekh%20is%20the%20India-Nepal-Tibet%20border%20and%20the%20area%20beyond%20that%20is%20not%20accessible%20to%20civilians.%20From%20here%2C%20one%20can%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Mount%20Kailash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdi%20Kailash%2C%20about%205%2C945%20metres%20tall%2C%20is%20in%20Pithoragarh%20district%20of%20Uttarakhand.%20The%20route%20to%20both%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20and%20Adi%20Kailash%20passes%20from%20Dharchula%2C%20but%20they%20separate%20from%20Gunji.%20While%20Adi%20Kailash%20is%20in%20India%2C%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20is%20situated%20in%20Tibet%2C%20which%20China%20claims%20as%20its%20own%20territory.%20Currently%2C%20Kailash%20Mansarovar%20yatra%20remains%20suspended%20due%20to%20multiple%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stretch%20from%20Dharchula%20to%20Tawaghat%20can%20be%20covered%20by%20road.%20The%20next%20mountainous%20stretch%2C%20which%20could%20earlier%20be%20covered%20only%20on%20foot%20and%20take%20around%208-10%20days%20to%20cover%2C%20can%20now%20be%20covered%20by%20car.%20The%20road%20not%20only%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20the%20pilgrims%2C%20but%20also%20opening%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJolikong%2C%20near%20Adi%20Kailash%2C%20has%20a%20base%20camp%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP).%20About%2040%20km%20from%20here%20is%20the%20border%20between%20India%2C%20Tibet%20and%20Nepal.%20This%20is%20till%20where%20civilians%20are%20allowed.%20Jolikong%20has%20very%20few%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdi%20Kailash%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20mountain%20where%20Shiva%20and%20Parvati%20had%20halted%20while%20going%20to%20take%20Samadhi%20on%20the%20Mount%20Kailash.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20locals%20believe%20there%20is%20a%20belief%20that%20there%20is%20a%20Parvati%20temple%20where%20she%20had%20taken%20bath.%20A%20pond%20remains%20symbolic%20of%20the%20mythological%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20visit%20the%20Adi%20Kailash%20temple%20and%20offer%20prayers%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%20He%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20the%20villagers%20in%20Gunji%20and%20offer%20prayers%20at%20Jageshwar%20temple%20in%20Almora%20district%20around%20noon.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20he%20will%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stones%20for%20several%20developmental%20projects%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697017920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fopn21s0o_adi-kailash-route_625x300_11_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-new-route-to-mount-kailash-viewpoint-lipulekh-in-uttarakhand-4470742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adi%20Kailash%2C%20located%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20is%20among%20the%20holiest%20sites%20for%20Hindus%2C%20and%20the%20route%20once%20included%20a%20long%20stretch%20that%20could%20only%20be%20covered%20on%20foot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-new-route-to-mount-kailash-viewpoint-lipulekh-in-uttarakhand-4470742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-new-route-to-mount-kailash-viewpoint-lipulekh-in-uttarakhand-4470742%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-new-route-to-mount-kailash-viewpoint-lipulekh-in-uttarakhand-4470742%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daily%20Despatch%3A%20US'%20Massive%20Moral%20And%20Military%20Support%20For%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F5smusvgg_daily-despatch-4_625x300_11_October_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20frontlines%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20NDTV%20brings%20you%20daily%20despatches%20by%20journalist%20Allan%20Sorensen%2C%20Middle%20East%20Correspondent%20for%20Danish%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad%2C%20giving%20insights%20and%20gripping%20first-hand%20accounts%20from%20the%20war-torn%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20after%20the%20deadly%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20villages%20in%20the%20southern%20parts%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20death%20count%20is%20spiralling%2C%20in%20both%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201%2C200%20Israelis%2C%20soldiers%20as%20well%20as%20civilians%2C%20have%20been%20killed.%20According%20to%20Gaza's%20health%20authorities%2C%20more%20than%20900%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20air%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20fighter%20jets%20continue%20to%20hit%20targets%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20Hamas%20is%20responding%20with%20rocket%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%20Israeli%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20Israel's%20jets%20hit%20the%20house%20of%20the%20parents%20of%20Muhammed%20Deif%2C%20a%20long-time%20military%20leader%20of%20Hamas%2C%20considered%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20Hamas%20attack%20last%20Saturday.%20The%20parents%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dramatic%20development%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20border%20crossing%20between%20Gaza%20and%20Egypt%20was%20hit%20twice%20by%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets.%20The%20crossing%20is%20closed%20for%20now%2C%20and%20in%20Gaza%2C%20around%20200%2C000%20people%20have%20left%20their%20homes%20to%20seek%20out%20safer%20places%20in%20open%20areas%20or%20UN%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20sporadic%20attacks%20in%20Israeli%20villages%20and%20cities%20have%20ceased.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20spokesperson%20says%20that%20Hamas%20fighters%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20from%20Gaza%20to%20Israel.%20According%20to%20the%20spokesperson%2C%20at%20least%201%2C500%20Hamas%20fighters%20have%20been%20killed%20inside%20Israel%20since%20Saturday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20northern%20border%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20the%20military%20build-up%20continues.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20300%2C000%20reservists%20called%20up%20for%20duty%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20Israel%20has%20called%20up%20an%20additional%2060%2C000%2C%20making%20it%20a%20total%20of%20360%2C000%20-%20the%20largest%20call-up%20of%20reservists%20in%20Israeli%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20northern%20border%20is%20witnessing%20a%20gradual%20daily%20escalation%20between%20the%20Lebanese%20Hezbollah%20militia%20and%20the%20Israeli%20army.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20an%20anti-tank%20missile%20was%20fired%20against%20an%20Israeli%20military%20position%20and%20after%20the%20Hezbollah%20had%20buried%20five%20of%20its%20fighters%2C%20who%20died%20in%20a%20firefight%20the%20previous%20day%2C%2012%20rockets%20were%20launched%20against%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20Israel.%20There%20were%20no%20casualties%2C%20but%20due%20to%20the%20gradual%20escalation%20the%20UNIFIL%20peacekeeping%20force%20in%20Lebanon%20has%20ordered%20its%20people%20to%20stay%20in%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emotional%20speech%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20US%20president%20Joe%20Biden%20expressed%20unprecedented%20moral%20and%20military%20support%20to%20Israel.%20He%20described%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20of%20sheer%20evil%26quot%3B%20and%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20ensure%20Israel%20has%20what%20it%20needs%20to%20respond%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20repeated%20that%20Israel%20will%20receive%20what%20it%20needs%20from%20the%20US%2C%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20current%20situation%20was%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20entire%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20butchered%20using%20their%20bodies%20to%20try%20to%20protect%20their%20children.%20Stomach-turning%20reports%20of%20babies%20being%20killed.%20Entire%20families%20slain.%20Young%20people%20were%20massacred%20while%20attending%20a%20musical%20festival%20to%20celebrate%20peace.%20Women%20raped%2C%20assaulted%2C%20paraded%20as%20trophies...%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20told%20the%20US%20President%20about%20the%20Hamas%20atrocities%20on%20a%20telephone%20call%20Biden's%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israeli%20media%20outlet%20Ynet%2C%20Netanyahu%20told%20Biden%20that%20the%20Hamas%20fighters%20beheaded%20soldiers%2C%20raped%20women%20and%20executed%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President's%20speech%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20biggest%20moral%20and%20military%20support%20to%20Israel%20since%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20nation%20in%201948.%20Biden%20confirmed%20that%20the%20US%20is%20sending%20a%20hangar%20ship%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20to%20assure%20Israel%20has%20what%20it%20needs%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20negotiations%20are%20on%20between%20political%20parties%20on%20the%20possible%20creation%20of%20an%20emergency%20government.%20Netanyahu%20has%20declared%20his%20readiness%20to%20establish%20a%20broad%20consensus%20government%20and%20has%20invited%20opposition%20parties%20to%20join.%20However%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20a%20government%20has%20been%20stalled%20so%20far%20due%20to%20demands%20from%20radical%20right-wing%20politician%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20National%20Security.%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir%20opposes%20the%20opposition%20getting%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Israeli%20security%20cabinet%20-%20a%20cabinet%20that%20makes%20crucial%20decisions%20during%20wartime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20over%20the%20emergency%20government%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20big%20headlines%20for%20Israeli%20media%20besides%20the%20ongoing%20fighting.%20The%20political%20establishment%20is%20being%20criticized%20broadly%20for%20not%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20create%20a%20broad%20government%20while%20Israel%20is%20on%20the%20path%20to%20a%20possible%20regional%20war.%20The%20political%20squabbling%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20reservists%20who%20are%20helping%20each%20other%20and%20standing%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%20ready%20to%20face%20Israel's%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETurkey%20has%20offered%20to%20mediate%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20to%20reach%20an%20end%20to%20the%20hostilities.%20Turkey%20also%20says%20it%20will%20help%20the%20two%20sides%20reach%20a%20possible%20agreement%20regarding%20hostage%20swaps.%20Some%20200%20are%20still%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bvicious%20circle%20of%20bloodshed%2C%20hatred%20and%20polarization%26quot%3B.%20But%20so%20far%2C%20there%20are%20no%20reports%20of%20any%20serious%20attempt%20to%20mediate%20a%20cease%20fire%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20It%20is%20still%20believed%20that%20Israel%20is%20preparing%20for%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%20Those%20preps%20could%20take%20days%2C%20if%20not%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20support%20for%20Israel%20is%20massive%20at%20the%20moment%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20many%20demonstrations%20in%20support%20of%20Gaza%20and%20Palestine%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20Western%20capitals.%20In%20Copenhagen%2C%20Denmark%2C%20flowers%20were%20laid%20next%20to%20the%20Israeli%20embassy%20in%20a%20show%20of%20sympathy%20to%20Israel%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20hours%20the%20flowers%20were%20taken%20and%20throw