sn't%20sure%20what%20Ashwin%20has%20done%20wrong%20to%20be%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Gavaskar%20also%20rued%20the%20absence%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20India's%20playing%20XI%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20a%20hat-trick%20against%20the%20same%20team%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20again%20Ashwin%20misses%20out%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20he%20has%20done%20wrong.%20He%20is%20used%20to%20being%20left%20out%20of%20the%20team.%20I%20thought%20what%20Shami%20had%20done%20against%20them%20(Afghanistan)%20in%202019%2C%20getting%20a%20hat-trick%2C%20he%20would%20get%20a%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20lost%20the%20toss%20and%20were%20asked%20by%20Afghanistan%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hashmatullah%20Shahidi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1685-hashmatullah-shaidi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHashmatullah%20Shahidi%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20field%20first.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20looking%20to%20bat%20second.%20We%20saw%20the%20amount%20of%20dew%20last%20evening.%20Don't%20think%20the%20wicket%20will%20change%20much.%20Need%20to%20bowl%20well%20and%20need%20to%20come%20back%20and%20bat%20better.%20We%20were%20under%20pressure%20(against%20Australia)%20to%20start%20with%2C%20but%20KL%20and%20Kohli%20batted%20well%2C%20they%20were%20magnificent%20and%20we%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20pride%20in%20our%20performance.%20It%20was%20a%20good%20game%20for%20us%2C%20hopefully%20we%20can%20repeat%20that%20and%20keep%20the%20momentum%20going%20forward.%20Ashwin%20misses%20out%2C%20Shardul%20Thakur%20comes%20in%20for%20him%2C'%20Rohit%20said%20after%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBarring%20the%20one%20change%20that%20saw%20Ashwin