mounts%20of%20veggies%20but%20keep%20moving%20to%20different%20areas%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20exhaust%20one%20area%E2%80%99s%20resources.%20Their%20excreta%20also%20nourishes%20the%20ground%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20for%20plants%20to%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20she%20believes%20humans%20should%20live%20in%20society.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20you%20take%20from%20nature%2C%20take%20it%20in%20a%20reasonable%20way%20and%20do%20not%20destroy%20it%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20idea%20that%20humans%20should%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%20just%20as%20elephants%20do%20in%20a%20forest%20is%20what%20gave%20the%20brand%20its%20name.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22he%20couple%20sells%20a%20ready-to-wear%20collection%20such%20as%20shirts%2C%20dresses%2C%20hoodies%20and%20bottoms%20in%20unbleached%20organic%20cotton%2C%20linen%20and%20hemp%20fabrics%20that%20use%20natural%20dyes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FEIY-3-1696946627-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20sells%20a%20ready-to-wear%20collection%20such%20as%20shirts%2C%20dresses%2C%20hoodies%20and%20bottoms%20in%20unbleached%20organic%20cotton%2C%20linen%20and%20hemp%20fabrics%20that%20use%20natural%20dyes.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Alankrutha%20Chandra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20their%20customers%2C%20Mahima%2C%20who%20recently%20purchased%20a%20dress%20from%20the%20brand%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20organic%20cotton%20and%20khadi%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20It%20is%20mainly%20for%20two%20reasons%2C%20they%20are%20environmentally-friendly%20and%20it%20supports%20the%20livelihood%20of%20farmers.%20While%20I%20love%20the%20fabrics%2C%20I%20could%20not%20find%20brands%20that%20have%20trendy%20designs.%20Most%20of%20them%20looked%20old-styled%20and%20out%20of%20fashion.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20search%20ended%20when%20I%20found%20Elephant%20In%20You%20in%20an%20exhibition.%20Alankrutha%E2%80%99s%20designs%20and%20clothes%20are%20very%20good%20and%20trendy.%20They%20are%20all%20organic%20and%20sustainable.%20The%20material%20and%20tailoring%20feels%20good%20on%20the%20skin.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20they%20not%20only%20deal%20in%20organic%20cotton%20but%20also%20hemp%20and%20linen%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20three%20years%20of%20moving%20to%20India%20and%20setting%20up%20the%20brand%20have%20been%20transformative%20for%20the%20couple.%20Looking%20back%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20brand%20is%20a%20reminder%20to%20society%20that%20we%20need%20to%20give%20back%20to%20nature%20as%20well.%20We%20have%20to%20stop%20producing%20waste%20and%20try%20to%20live%20a%20slow%20and%20sustainable%20life.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20living%20sustainably%20now%2C%20we%20will%20lose%20the%20amazing%20resources%20that%20nature%20has%20to%20offer.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696948290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22origin