d%20Hanuman%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20every%20household%20in%20the%20village%20has%20a%20football%20player%2C%20it%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Mini%20Brazil%E2%80%99%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20journey%20of%20Bicharpur%20village%20from%20its%20miserable%20state%20to%20%E2%80%98Mini%20Brazil%E2%80%99%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20former%20footballer%20and%20coach%20Raees%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20unlikely%20football%20hub%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaees%20says%20that%20the%20Shahdol%20division%20has%20been%20a%20football%20hub%20for%20nearly%20three%20generations.%20The%20tribal%20children%20grew%20up%20playing%20football%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20Raaes%2C%20who%20has%20been%20playing%20football%20since%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20was%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20learn%20football%20by%20seeing%20players%20in%20tournaments.%20But%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20or%20guidance%20in%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2053-year-old%20who%20grew%20up%20following%20Diego%20Armando%20Maradona%20%E2%80%94%20a%20professional%20football%20player%20from%20Argentina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tribal%20children%20grew%20up%20playing%20football%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20training.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ffootball-bicharpur-5-1696858393-50