knock%20down%20a%20perpetrator%20within%20minutes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331726%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20vigour%20comes%20from%20within%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F57380%2Fsimple-self-defense-techniques-everyone-needs-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20self-defence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Asha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSelf-defence%20is%2090%20percent%20mental%20and%20only%2010%20percent%20physical.%20It%20is%20just%20about%20your%20determination%20that%20comes%20from%20within.%20Girls%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20weak%20physically%20so%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20fight%20men.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20trained%20enough%2C%20you%20can%20protect%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions%20where%20each%20session%20is%20split%20into%20six%20days.%20Explaining%20her%20strategy%20to%20train%20girls%20with%20disabilities%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTraining%20them%20is%20a%20little%20different%20as%20they%20can%20only%20sense%20someone%20by%20touch%20while%20abled%20persons%20can%20perceive%20danger%20by%20seeing%20the%20perpetrator%20or%20even%20hearing%20their%20conversations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20girls%20with%20disabilities%2C%20I%20utilise%20daily%20work%20experiences%20like%20brushing%20teeth%20or%20kicking%20a%20football%20into%20attack%20positions.%20By%20using%20a%20dummy%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20if%20they%20sense%20danger%20from%20behind%20them%2C%20they%20then%20could%20hit%20them%20by%20bending%20their%20elbow%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%20when%20they%20brush%20their%20teeth.%20Or%20they%20could%20kick%20them%20like%20they%20would%20kick%20a%20football.%20When%20they%20hit%20the%20dummy%20themselves%2C%20they%20build%20confidence.%20With%20training%2C%20they%20learn%20how%20they%20could%20convert%20their%20body%20into%20a%20weapon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20students%20to%20try%20negotiations%20first.%20%3Cem%3EPar%20agar%20baaton%20se%20kaam%20na%20chale%2C%20to%20laaton%20se%20kaam%20chalao.%20Aur%20laton%20pe%20aa%20jaaye%20to%20jhukna%20nahi%20hai.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(But%20when%20negotiations%20fail%20to%20work%2C%20hit%20them%20hard%2C%20and%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20that%2C%20then%20there%20should%20be%20no%20backing%20down)%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20such%20incident%2C%20Asha%20explains%20how%20she%20once%20saw%20a%20girl%20dragging%20a%20%3Cem%3Echhora%3C%2Fem%3E%20(boy)%20by%20his%20shirt%E2%80%99s%20collar%20and%20bringing%20him%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20told%20me%20how%20he%20passed%20comments%20on%20her.%20The%20guy%20apologised%20to%20us%20and%20even%20pledged%20not%20to%20flirt%20with%20any%20woman%20ever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20so%20satisfying%20to%20see%20this%20confidence%20among%20girls.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20women%20have%20come%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20empowered%20themselves.%20I%20have%20seen%20girls%20coming%20in%20trucks%20from%20villages%2030%20km%20away%20to%20learn%20self-defence%20from%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20work%2C%20Asha%20does%20not%20charge%20a%20penny.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20%3Cem%3Eguru%20dakshina%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tuition%20fees%20of%20a%20teacher)%20from%20these%20students%20is%20that%20they%20pledge%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20their%20own%20safety%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20someone%20else%20like%20their%20father%20or%20brothers.%20Every%20woman%20must%20know%20safety%20rules%20and%20develop%20safety%20skills%20irrespective%20of%20their%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Asha%20was%20recognised%20at%20a%20State%20Level%20Teacher%20Award%20Ceremony%20by%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20for%20her%20work.%20She%20was%20also%20conferred%20the%20Ambedkar%20Mahila%20Puraskar%20Award%202023.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20on%20September%205%2C%20she%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20recognition%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20training%20young%20girls%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20is%20paramount%20for%20Asha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20this%20work%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20personal%20happiness.%20Now%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20girls%20I%20trained%20will%20be%20able%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20humiliation%20that%20was%20once%20caused%20to%20one%20of%20my%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F1679310394CII2021Volume1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECrime%20In%20India%202021%20Volume%20I%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Asha%20Suman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696603084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1-1696597320.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alwar's%20Asha%20Suman%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20imparting%20self-defence%20skills%20to%20young%20girls.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20trained%2030%2C000%20girls%20across%20Rajasthan.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20she%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331721%2Frajasthan-government-school-teacher-trains-self-defense-to-girls-with-disabilities-national-award%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Me%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Patients%20of%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20Want%20India%20to%20Learn%20About%20Their%20Condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20say%20that%20I%20could%20walk%20as%20a%20toddler%20but%20over%20time%2C%20I%20started%20losing%20balance.%20I%20would%20fall%20over%2C%20my%20spine%20became%20slightly%20curved%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20assistance%20with%20daily%20activities.%20My%20parents%20ran%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20a%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20recounts%20Priya%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20Lucknow-based%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20disability%20rights%20activist%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20has%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20(SMA)%20Type-II.%20Such%20is%20the%20story%20of%20many%20people%20with%20the%20rare%2C%20progressive%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20when%2014-month-old%20Roha%20began%20experiencing%20trouble%20breathing%2C%20her%20parents%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20another%20town.%20After%20two%20weeks%2C%20multiple%20tests%20and%20misdiagnoses%20later%2C%20they%20were%20shattered%20to%20know%20that%20their%20little%20daughter%20had%20the%20fatal%20illness.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20heard%20of%20SMA%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20meant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20SMA%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20much%20awareness%20of%20the%20condition%20even%20among%20medical%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaran%20Shah%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20canine%20and%20feline%20behaviourist%2C%20was%20misdiagnosed%20with%20polio%20shortly%20after%20birth.%20However%2C%20he%20got%20a%20diagnosis%20after%20his%20mother%20insisted%20on%20getting%20him%20tested%20for%20the%20condition.%20He%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Pawsitivve%20Future%2C%20a%20canine%20training%20centre%2C%20and%20lives%20with%20SMA%20Type-III.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20a%20drastic%20impact%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20get%20to%20know%20more%20about%20this%20condition%20that%20creates%20significant%20impairment%20and%20results%20in%20a%20locomotor%20disability.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295507%2Fdisability-inclusive-policy-at-workplaces-lessons-from-accenture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAwareness%20is%20the%20first%20step%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20the%20cause%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20including%20raising%20funds%20for%20its%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201075px)%20100vw%2C%201075px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20there's%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%201075w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20SMA%20and%20whom%20does%20it%20affect%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESMA%20is%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20impacts%20the%20control%20of%20muscle%20movement.%20It%20mainly%20affects%20the%20spinal%20region%20while%20the%20muscles%20of%20peripheral%20internal%20organs%20are%20relatively%20unaffected.%20SMA%20is%20a%20progressive%20condition%20that%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20muscle%20wastage%20or%20atrophy%20in%20the%20body.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20globally%2C%201%20in%20every%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Fdls%2Fnsmbb_sma.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSpinal%2520Muscular%2520Atrophy%2520(SMA)%2520is%2Cbeing%2520unable%2520to%2520make%2520protein.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20SMA%2C%20while%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asterhospitals.in%2Fblogs-events-news%2Faster-cmi-bangalore%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy-types-symptoms-and-treatment%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSMA%2520is%2520a%2520relatively%2520rare%2Caround%25203%252C200%2520newborns%2520every%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%2C200%20infants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20born%20with%20the%20condition%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mda.org%2Fdisease%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy%2Fcauses-inheritance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuscular%20Dystrophy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SMA%20is%20caused%20by%20missing%20or%20mutated%20SMN1%20or%20SMN2%20genes%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20survival%20muscle%20neuron%20genes.%20The%20protein%20produced%20by%20this%20gene%20%E2%80%94%20SMN%20protein%20%E2%80%94%20facilitates%20movement%20and%20is%20needed%20by%20motor%20neurons%20to%20function%20effectively.%20Since%20the%20gene%20is%20faulty%20or%20missing%2C%20it%20impedes%20movement%20among%20those%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20SMA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindividuals%20experience%20several%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20voluntary%20movements%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20head%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20limbs.%20Priya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20spinal%20cord%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20are%20affected%2C%20people%20with%20SMA%20also%20develop%20scoliosis%20or%20spinal%20curvature.%20I%20have%20it%20too%20and%20I%20manage%20it%20by%20stuffing%20a%20lot%20of%20cushions%20around%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20limited%20mobility%2C%20I%20have%20low%20muscle%20tone%20which%20results%20in%20weaker%20bone%20health%20and%20density.%20Even%20lifting%20a%20book%20seems%20like%20a%20Herculean%20task%20to%20me.%20My%20condition%20also%20makes%20me%20prone%20to%20frequent%20fractures%20and%20joint%20dislocations.%20Since%20my%20mobility%20is%20impacted%2C%20I%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20to%20move%20around%20and%20need%20support%20with%20activities%20of%20daily%20living.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Priya%2C%20many%20others%20with%20SMA%20require%20wheelchairs%20too.%20They%20may%20also%20rely%20on%20different%20support%20needs%20for%20daily%20life.%20Some%20patients%20have%20difficulty%20in%20swallowing%20and%20eating%20food%20and%20may%20require%20a%20feeding%20tube%20while%20others%20with%20compromised%20lungs%20may%20need%20breathing%20support%20or%20ventilation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-300x175.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-500x292.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-768x448.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-150x88.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331662%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Priya%2C%20her%20caregiver%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20my%20parents%20have%20aged%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20them%20to%20lift%20me%20up%2C%20carry%20me%20around%20or%20support%20my%20needs.%20If%20my%20caregiver%20goes%20on%20a%20leave%20for%20even%20one%20day%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20my%20mother%20and%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20of%20everyday%20activities%20seem%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recounts%20how%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20people%20give%20unsolicited%20advice%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%20about%20managing%20her%20disability%20without%20realising%20none%20of%20them%20work%20because%20her%20body%20functions%20differently%20than%20other%20people%E2%80%99s.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20while%20travelling%20in%20a%20car%20or%20plane%2C%20someone%20must%20hold%20me%20tightly%20because%20even%20the%20slightest%20of%20jerks%20can%20make%20me%20fall%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Alpana%20Sharma%2C%20caring%20for%20her%2011-year-old%20son%20Aarav%2C%20who%20has%20SMA%20Type-II%2C%20has%20been%20an%20exhausting%20process.%20With%20managing%20doctors%E2%80%99%20appointments%2C%20therapy%20and%20everything%20else%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20mother%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%98why%20me%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20stigma%20of%20a%20genetic%20condition%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20our%20friends%20cut%20ties%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20festive%20celebration%2C%20Alpana%20recounts%2C%20a%20woman%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20her%20child%20eat%20the%20%3Cem%3Eprasad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20offered%20to%20a%20deity)%20being%20distributed%20by%20Aarav%2C%20in%20fear%20of%20contacting%20SMA%20from%20him.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20cannot%20pour%20from%20an%20empty%20cup%2C%20so%20I%20invested%20my%20energy%20and%20time%20in%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20abilities.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20helps%20both%20of%20us%20stay%20positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlpana%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curesmaindia.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank